      VisibleName: Sohva
      ArtisticDescription: "Teemana on Taakka. Sen voi tulkita monella tapaa, mutta
        huonekaluista on tarkoitus tulla painava vaikutelma. V\xE4rit mukailevat
        Atlas-titaanin patsasta."
      EnglishArtisticDescription: The theme is burden. It can be interpreted in multiple
        ways, but the goal of the furnitures is to create a weighty impression. The
        colors are inspired by the statue of the titan Atlas
