    ArtistName: SMKT
    list:
    - Name: Sink
      EnglishName: Sink
      Image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a521397346aa25e4cab9e4a0252a080c, type: 3}
      PosterImage: {fileID: 0}
      RibbonImage: {fileID: 0}
      VisibleName: Lavuaari
      ArtisticDescription: "- mit\xE4 kaikkea joutuu itsest\xE4\xE4n piilottamaan
        nyt ja historiassa (esim. noitavainot, alkemistit, paranormaaliin uskominen)
        ettei tule leimatuksi mielisairaaksi tms. - kenest\xE4k\xE4\xE4n ei voi tiet\xE4\xE4
        mit\xE4 joku piilottelee. - miksi juuri wc-huonekalut (osalle turvapaikka
        kodinkin sis\xE4ll\xE4, esim. oven saa lukkoon)"
      EnglishArtisticDescription: '- What are the things people have to hide from
        themselves now and in history (For example, witch hunts, alchemists, believers
        of paranormal activities) in order for them to avoid being labeled mentally
        ill. - You can never know what someone is hiding. - But why exactly toilet
        furniture (which acts as a haven for some, even inside their own home, for
        example, they can lock their doors)'
      DiagnoseNumber: F20
      BaseFurniture:
        Name: Sink_Schrodinger
        Rarity: 0
        FurnitureSize: {x: 2, y: 2, z: 1}
        Placement: 1
        Weight: 13
        Value: 150
        Material: 
        Recycling: 
